WEBVTT

00:03:28.272 --> 00:03:32.312
nude bathing with men present.

00:03:32.312 --> 00:03:33.867
Where they have no place

00:03:33.867 --> 00:03:35.176
is where the men are:

00:03:35.176 --> 00:03:36.166
in the Forum,

00:03:36.166 --> 00:03:37.168
in the Law Court,

00:03:37.168 --> 00:03:39.106
or in the Senate House.

00:03:39.122 --> 00:03:42.079
Their place in public is in the porticos

00:03:42.079 --> 00:03:43.120
with gardens,

00:03:43.120 --> 00:03:44.295
with sculpture,

00:03:44.295 --> 00:03:47.337
and with pathways for walking in.

00:03:47.337 --> 00:03:49.718
When Domitia, Domitia, and Domitia want

00:03:49.718 --> 00:03:51.474
to leave the house to go somewhere,

00:03:51.474 --> 00:03:53.670
like the Portico of Livia,

00:03:53.670 --> 00:03:55.145
they must get ready.

00:03:55.145 --> 00:03:58.211
Domitia II and Domitia III are ready,

00:03:58.211 --> 00:04:01.064
but Domitia I, who is betrothed to be married